data.title: Dive into anything
data.text:
On top of that, the logo doesn't scream "happy bunnies and cookies". Even the OG one from Blake's flashback seems pretty disturbing. I'm no graphic designer, but "Angry Grimm thingy" probably is not an ideal mascot for your peaceful protest group.

Clearly Blake is a brainwashed sleeper agent or something, and the White Fang was always antagonistic to humanity.
